Package: because
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Estimation of Causal Effects
Version: 0.9.7
Authors@R: c(
    person(
      "Achaz", "von Hardenberg",
      email = "achaz.hardenberg@unipv.it",
      role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
  )
Description: Provides tools for specifying and fitting Bayesian Structural Equation Models
    using JAGS. The 'because' package allows causal inference in complex ecological and 
    evolutionary analyses, accounting for phylogenetic uncertainty, spatial autocorrelation, 
    and other covariance structures. Implements and expands on the methods described in
    von Hardenberg and Gonzalez-Voyer (2025) <doi:10.1111/2041-210X.70044>.
SystemRequirements: JAGS (>= 4.0.0)
License: AGPL-3
